---
title: Chipotle-Roasted Cauliflower Tacos with Feta, Avocado and DIY Pickled Shallots
description: In a hurry? These chipotle-roasted cauliflower tacos will be on the table in no time!  Avocado, pickled shallots, and feta add a rainbow of flavour to the roasted cauliflower. Wrap it up in a warm tortilla and hit the road.
